{
  "texts": [
    "The basic network construction unit is the Residual-in-Residual Dense Block (RRDB) without batch normalization.AlphaGAN [33] invented by Lutz et al.",
    "developed a generator network that predicts appealing alphas using adversarial loss from the discriminator that recognises well-composed photos.",
    "Dilated convolutions improve encoder-decoder architectures for convolutional neural networks (CNN) spatial localisation by collecting global context information without downscaling feature maps or sacrificing spatial information.",
    "Misc-GAN [34] discovered by Zhou et al.",
    "describe the hierarchical distribution of graph structures at different granularities and \"transfer\" it from the graphs in the region of interest to a unique graph representation."
  ]
}